seo: 用友FE,目录遍历漏洞,templateOfTaohong_manager.jsp,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测用友FE协作办公平台中templateOfTaohong_manager.jsp文件是否存在目录遍历漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断是否存在风险。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the directory traversal vulnerability in the templateOfTaohong_manager.jsp file of Yonyou FE collaborative office platform. It determines whether there is a risk by sending specific requests.
